text: Jorge Llambí (born 7 March 1939) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1971 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
